{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "https://excalidraw.com", "elements": [{"id": "title", "type": "text", "x": 60, "y": 30, "width": 1600, "height": 50, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#111827", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "hachure", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": null, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "多 Agent 分Tag执行闭环：Airtable真源 → Agent认领 → GitHub+Feishu产出 → 回写证据 → Dashboard追踪", "fontSize": 30, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 30, "containerId": null, "originalText": "多 Agent 分Tag执行闭环：Airtable真源 → Agent认领 → GitHub+Feishu产出 → 回写证据 → Dashboard追踪", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "r1", "type": "rectangle", "x": 70, "y": 110, "width": 620, "height": 540, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#5b6ca8", "backgroundColor": "#f4f7ff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "t1", "type": "text", "x": 100, "y": 140, "width": 560, "height": 470, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#334155", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "hachure", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": null, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "① 真源层｜Airtable + Dashboard\n\nAirtable Tasks 是唯一真源\n字段：\n- title / desc\n- state(ToDo/Doing/Done/Blocked)\n- tag / owner / update_at\n\nDashboard 负责：\n- 任务可视化\n- 按tag检索\n- 进度追踪与验收\n\n规则：\n所有关键进展必须回写，\n避免信息分叉。", "fontSize": 34, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 34, "containerId": null, "originalText": "① 真源层｜Airtable + Dashboard\n\nAirtable Tasks 是唯一真源\n字段：\n- title / desc\n- state(ToDo/Doing/Done/Blocked)\n- tag / owner / update_at\n\nDashboard 负责：\n- 任务可视化\n- 按tag检索\n- 进度追踪与验收\n\n规则：\n所有关键进展必须回写，\n避免信息分叉。", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "r2", "type": "rectangle", "x": 760, "y": 110, "width": 760, "height": 540, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#9b6ac8", "backgroundColor": "#faf5ff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "t2", "type": "text", "x": 790, "y": 140, "width": 700, "height": 500, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#4c1d95", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "hachure", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": null, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "② 执行层｜Sam主脑 + 4个Agent\n\nSam（主脑）：\n- 最终判断与仲裁\n- 统一优先级与质量标准\n\nAndrew（AI学习）\n- AI Collection / AI Solid Knowledge\n输出：学习卡 / 观点 / 论文解析\n\nRex（工作 + CER）\n- R·Agent / 全栈开发 / RAify\n输出：代码方案 / 路演结构 / 执行复盘\n\nLulu（输出生产）\n- She Codes Herself\n输出：文案 / 视频脚本 / 发布复盘\n\nAlex（个人成长）\n- 思维宫殿\n输出：Daily / Weekly / 行动卡", "fontSize": 32, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 32, "containerId": null, "originalText": "② 执行层｜Sam主脑 + 4个Agent\n\nSam（主脑）：\n- 最终判断与仲裁\n- 统一优先级与质量标准\n\nAndrew（AI学习）\n- AI Collection / AI Solid Knowledge\n输出：学习卡 / 观点 / 论文解析\n\nRex（工作 + CER）\n- R·Agent / 全栈开发 / RAify\n输出：代码方案 / 路演结构 / 执行复盘\n\nLulu（输出生产）\n- She Codes Herself\n输出：文案 / 视频脚本 / 发布复盘\n\nAlex（个人成长）\n- 思维宫殿\n输出：Daily / Weekly / 行动卡", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "r3", "type": "rectangle", "x": 760, "y": 700, "width": 760, "height": 540, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#4c9b85", "backgroundColor": "#f1fdf8", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "t3", "type": "text", "x": 790, "y": 730, "width": 700, "height": 450, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#065f46", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "hachure", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": null, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "③ 产出层｜Feishu Wiki + GitHub\n\nFeishu Wiki（协作稿）\n- 结构化总结\n- 草稿页（... - Sam）\n- 复盘与模板沉淀\n\nGitHub（交付资产）\n- 代码\n- PPT\n- 图片\n- 文字与表格文件\n\n双向链接规则：\n- GitHub链接写回同名Wiki\n- Wiki/GitHub证据写回Task Desc", "fontSize": 32, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 32, "containerId": null, "originalText": "③ 产出层｜Feishu Wiki + GitHub\n\nFeishu Wiki（协作稿）\n- 结构化总结\n- 草稿页（... - Sam）\n- 复盘与模板沉淀\n\nGitHub（交付资产）\n- 代码\n- PPT\n- 图片\n- 文字与表格文件\n\n双向链接规则：\n- GitHub链接写回同名Wiki\n- Wiki/GitHub证据写回Task Desc", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "r4", "type": "rectangle", "x": 70, "y": 700, "width": 620, "height": 540, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#cc7a3a", "backgroundColor": "#fff7ef", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "t4", "type": "text", "x": 100, "y": 730, "width": 560, "height": 470, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#9a3412", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "hachure", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": null, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "text": "④ 反馈层｜回写 + 验收\n\n统一回写：\n- Deliverable\n- Feishu Link\n- GitHub Link\n- Owner / Status / Next\n\n执行节奏：\n- 实时进展即回写\n- EOD只做汇总\n\n管理收益：\n- 看板可诊断\n- 交付可追溯\n- 复盘可复用\n\n一句话：\n“不是只聊流程，\n而是交付持续推进。”", "fontSize": 34, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 34, "containerId": null, "originalText": "④ 反馈层｜回写 + 验收\n\n统一回写：\n- Deliverable\n- Feishu Link\n- GitHub Link\n- Owner / Status / Next\n\n执行节奏：\n- 实时进展即回写\n- EOD只做汇总\n\n管理收益：\n- 看板可诊断\n- 交付可追溯\n- 复盘可复用\n\n一句话：\n“不是只聊流程，\n而是交付持续推进。”", "lineHeight": 1.25}, {"id": "a12", "type": "arrow", "x": 700, "y": 380, "width": 50, "height": 0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "hachure", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": {"type": 2}, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "points": [[0, 0], [50, 0]], "lastCommittedPoint": [50, 0], "startBinding": null, "endBinding": null, "startArrowhead": null, "endArrowhead": "arrow"}, {"id": "a23", "type": "arrow", "x": 1140, "y": 660, "width": 0, "height": 30, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "hachure", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "roundness": {"type": 2}, "seed": 1, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "points": [[0, 0], [0, 30]], "lastCommittedPoint": [0, 30], "startBinding": null, "endBinding": null, "startArrowhead": null, "endArrowhead": "arrow"}, {"id": "a34", "type": "arrow", "x": 760, "y": 970, "width": -60, "height": 0, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "hachure", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacit